    <h1 className="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-5xl dark:text-white">
      <span
        data-testid="title"
        className="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-conic-l from-yellow-500 via-purple-500 to-blue-500"
      >
        Hey, I’m Oscar te Giffel
      </span>
    </h1>
    <h2 className="mb-16 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-100">
      I’m a developer, aspired writer, and creator. I work at HeadFWD as a Fullstack Software Consultant. You have found
      my website where I aspire to start writing and sharing things I have learned.
